sources.src/sass/main.sass:
@import reset

//     (400, 500, 700 font-w)
// font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif

$mainfont: 'Poppins', sans-serif

//  color  //
$accentcolor: #FF9900
$titlecolor: #2F281E
$textcolor: #544837
//  color  //

body
    font-family: $mainfont
    font-weight: 500
    font-size: 16px
    line-height: 26px
    color: $textcolor

button
    font-family: $mainfont
    font-weight: 700
a
    text-decoration: none
    outline: none !important

.header
    // height: 100px

.container
    max-width: 1124px
    margin: 0 auto
    padding: 0 10px

.header_inner
    display: flex
    justify-content: space-between
    align-items: center
    height: 78px

.header_menu
    margin-left: auto

.menu_list
    display: flex

.menu_list-item + .menu_list-item
    margin-left: 25px

.list_item-link
    font-size: 14px
    line-height: 28px
    font-weight: 400
    color: $titlecolor
    &.item_link-active
        text-decoration: underline

.header_nav
    margin-left: 55px

.header_nav-links + .header_nav-links
    margin-left: 14px

.header_nav-links
    padding: 10px 25px
    font-size: 16px
    color: #173A56
    line-height: 24px
    font-weight: 600
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, .1)
    border-radius: 4px
    background: #ffffff
    &:last-child
        background: $accentcolor
        color: #FFFFFF
        border-color: transparent

.top_inner
    background-image: url(../img/top-img.png)
    background-repeat: no-repeat
    background-position: bottom right
    padding: 133px 0 80px 0

.top_title
    color: $titlecolor
    font-weight: 700
    font-size: 44px
    line-height: 54px
    margin-bottom: 30px
    max-width: 518px

.top_text
    font-size: 18px
    line-height: 28px
    font-weight: 400
    max-width: 460px
    margin-bottom: 45px

.top_btn
    background: $accentcolor
    border-radius: 4px
    padding: 15px 40px
    font-size: 16px
    line-height: 24px
    display: inline-block
    color: #ffffff
    border: none
    margin-right: 30px
.top_link
    line-height: 24px
    display: inline-block
    color: $accentcolor
    text-decoration: underline
    font-weight: 600
    padding-left: 25px
    position: relative
    &::before
        content: ""
        position: absolute
        left: 0
        bottom: 3px
        width: 17px
        height: 19px
        background-image: url(../img/topvideo-play.svg)

.tools
    padding-top: 110px

.tools-title
    color: $titlecolor
    font-weight: 700
    font-size: 36px
    line-height: 54px
    text-align: center
    max-width: 540px
    margin: 0 auto 46px
    padding: 0 10px

.tools_inner
    background: url(../img/topinnerbg.svg) bottom center no-repeat
    background-size: cover
    padding-bottom: 90px

.tools_items
    display: flex
    justify-content: space-between
    padding: 8px 16px 0
    margin-bottom: 60px

.tools_item
    width: 240px

.tools_item-img
    margin-bottom: 30px

.tools_item-title
    color: $titlecolor
    font-size: 22px
    line-height: 33px
    font-weight: 600
    margin-bottom: 13px

.tools_link
    padding: 15px 32px 14px
    border-radius: 4px
    display: block
    background: $accentcolor
    line-height: 24px
    color: #ffffff
    font-weight: 700
    width: 173px
    margin: 0 auto

.direction
    padding: 120px 0 100px 0

.direction_item
    display: flex
    justify-content: space-between
    margin-bottom: 100px

.direction_item-content
    max-width: 486px

.direction_item-shorttitle
    line-height: 24px
    margin-bottom: 3px

.direction_item-title
    font-size: 36px
    line-height: 54px
    font-weight: 700
    color: $titlecolor
    margin-bottom: 22px
.direction_item-text
    margin-bottom: 25px
.direction_item-subtitle
    font-weight: 700
    color: $titlecolor
    margin-bottom: 12px

.reverse
    display: flex
    flex-direction: row-reverse

.direction_list-item
    margin-bottom: 30px
    padding-left: 65px
    position: relative
    &::before
        content: ""
        position: absolute
        background-image: url(../img/ul-reverse.svg)
        width: 35px
        height: 35px
        left: 0
        top: 7

.team
    background: url("../img/teamOval.svg") top center no-repeat 
    background-size: cover
    padding: 230px 0 380px

.team_inner
    position: relative

.team_item
    position: absolute
    width: 98px
    height: 98px
    right: 80px
    top: 157px
.team_box
    max-width: 542px
    margin: 0 auto
    text-align: center

.team_title
    color: $titlecolor
    font-size: 36px
    line-height: 54px
    font-weight: 700
    margin-bottom: 22px

.team_text
    color:#567592
    margin-bottom: 45px

.team_btn
    background-color: $accentcolor
    border: none
    border-radius: 4px
    padding: 15px 30px
    color: #ffffff

.team_item-text
    background-color: #ffffff
    padding: 14px 20px 15px
    display: inline-block
    color: $titlecolor
    box-shadow: 0px 2px 15px rgba(23, 58, 86, 0.1)
    border-radius: 26px
    position: absolute
    top: 0px
    right: 0px
